  <main>
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="top">
        <div>
          <h1>Private Coaching Framework</h1>
          <p class="sub">
            Coaching is built around a structured process: establish baselines, define the shot pattern, apply targeted interventions, and verify transfer on the course. Every track includes measurable checkpoints and a clear next step.
          </p>
        </div>
        <a class="btn primary" href="contact.html">Book a Lesson</a>
      </div>

      <div class="grid" aria-label="Instruction offerings">
        <!-- Junior -->
        <article class="card">
          <div class="badge"><i></i>Junior Development Model</div>
          <h2>Junior Development Model</h2>
          <p>Designed to build athletic foundations, resilient technique, and confidence—while keeping progress measurable and age-appropriate.</p>

          <div class="cols">
            <div class="mini"><b>Who it’s for</b><span>Beginners through competitive juniors; families seeking a clear pathway.</span></div>
            <div class="mini"><b>Expected outcome</b><span>Stronger fundamentals, consistent contact, and a clear progression plan.</span></div>
            <div class="mini"><b>Structured process</b><span>Skill benchmarks → training blocks → progress reviews → pathway placement.</span></div>
            <div class="mini"><b>Focus points</b><span>Movement, ball flight control, scoring skills, competitive routines.</span></div>
          </div>

          <div class="actions">
            <a class="btn primary" href="contact.html">Book Junior Session</a>
            <a class="btn" href="academy.html">View Academy Levels</a>
          </div>
        </article>

        <!-- Adult -->
        <article class="card">
          <div class="badge"><i></i>Adult Performance Coaching</div>
          <h2>Adult Performance Coaching</h2>
          <p>For players who want a repeatable pattern and a scoring model that translates to the course—without guesswork.</p>

          <div class="cols">
            <div class="mini"><b>Who it’s for</b><span>Committed recreational golfers and competitive amateurs.</span></div>
            <div class="mini"><b>Expected outcome</b><span>More predictable ball flight and improved scoring decisions.</span></div>
            <div class="mini"><b>Structured process</b><span>Shot pattern audit → root cause diagnosis → drills → on-course verification.</span></div>
            <div class="mini"><b>Focus points</b><span>Start line, curvature control, wedge benchmarks, putting routines.</span></div>
          </div>

          <div class="actions">
            <a class="btn primary" href="contact.html">Book Adult Session</a>
            <a class="btn" href="contact.html">Request a Consultation</a>
          </div>
        </article>

        <!-- High Performance -->
        <article class="card">
          <div class="badge"><i></i>High Performance Training</div>
          <h2>High Performance Training</h2>
          <p>Optimization for competitive players: speed, pressure training, and technical refinement aligned to performance goals.</p>

          <div class="cols">
            <div class="mini"><b>Who it’s for</b><span>High school, tournament juniors, and serious competitors.</span></div>
            <div class="mini"><b>Expected outcome</b><span>More distance with control, better scoring under pressure, stronger routines.</span></div>
            <div class="mini"><b>Structured process</b><span>Testing → training blocks → performance review → tournament plan.</span></div>
            <div class="mini"><b>Focus points</b><span>Speed protocols, dispersion, decision-making, resilience, prep.</span></div>
          </div>

          <div class="actions">
            <a class="btn primary" href="contact.html">Book Performance Block</a>
            <a class="btn" href="academy.html">SGCC High School Track</a>
          </div>
        </article>

        <!-- On-Course -->
        <article class="card">
          <div class="badge"><i></i>On-Course Strategy Coaching</div>
          <h2>On-Course Strategy Coaching</h2>
          <p>Because scoring is a skill. Train decisions, targets, and routines where performance actually happens.</p>

          <div class="cols">
            <div class="mini"><b>Who it’s for</b><span>Players who practice well but don’t score to capability.</span></div>
            <div class="mini"><b>Expected outcome</b><span>Better target selection, fewer big numbers, stronger conversion.</span></div>
            <div class="mini"><b>Structured process</b><span>Dispersion mapping → shot selection rules → review of outcomes.</span></div>
            <div class="mini"><b>Focus points</b><span>Approach strategy, wedge decisions, risk profile, routines.</span></div>
          </div>

          <div class="actions">
            <a class="btn primary" href="contact.html">Book On-Course</a>
            <a class="btn" href="contact.html">Ask About Packages</a>
          </div>
        </article>

        <!-- Winter -->
        <article class="card">
          <div class="badge"><i></i>Winter Indoor Performance Programs</div>
          <h2>Winter Indoor Performance Programs</h2>
          <p>Structured off-season development: maintain feel, build speed, and refine scoring skills through measurable training blocks.</p>

          <div class="cols">
            <div class="mini"><b>Who it’s for</b><span>Juniors and adults seeking momentum through the off-season.</span></div>
            <div class="mini"><b>Expected outcome</b><span>Cleaner contact, improved speed metrics, better spring readiness.</span></div>
            <div class="mini"><b>Structured process</b><span>Baseline testing → weekly plan → checkpoints → transition plan.</span></div>
            <div class="mini"><b>Focus points</b><span>Speed, strike, start-line control, wedge/putt skills.</span></div>
          </div>

          <div class="actions">
            <a class="btn primary" href="contact.html">Book Winter Program</a>
            <a class="btn" href="academy.html">View Seasonal Programming</a>
          </div>
        </article>

        <!-- Placeholder for additional -->
        <article class="card">
          <div class="badge"><i></i>Structured Development</div>
          <h2>What You Can Expect</h2>
          <p>Every plan is built to reduce noise and increase clarity—so you leave each session knowing exactly what matters and how to train it.</p>
          <div class="cols">
            <div class="mini"><b>Baseline</b><span>Identify current pattern + scoring profile.</span></div>
            <div class="mini"><b>Plan</b><span>Define the training block with priorities.</span></div>
            <div class="mini"><b>Training</b><span>High-quality reps with clear intent.</span></div>
            <div class="mini"><b>Transfer</b><span>Verify performance in real conditions.</span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="actions">
            <a class="btn primary" href="contact.html">Start Here</a>
            <a class="btn" href="about.html">View Credentials</a>
          </div>
        </article>
